HEADWORD: Byway
<hw>By"way`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A secluded, private,
or obscure way; a path or road aside from the main one.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧
Take no <xex>byways.</xex>⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Herbert.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

